description:
New for 2022, the Webb Telescope Tracker provides regularly updated data from the historic James Webb Telescope as it leaves earth to explore the galaxy!
Since the API I was using has gone down, I've switched to a periodic (roughly weekly) manual refresh on data and images. Pre3 is now supported.
versionNote:
1.0.0 - Initial release - my first from-scratch Enyo app
1.0.1 - The telescope has arrived in its final orbit, so the data source has gone stale. At least for now, this update handles end of life for the API.
1.0.2 - Back-to-life... with periodic data updates!
